    "1. After the initial setup, create another **OAuth client ID** in the same project." : {
      "comment" : "Context: Settings > Syncing. Surrounding UI explains Google Drive setup, then shows sync direction, auto-sync, Client ID, status, sign-out, and connect controls. Preserve product names and Markdown.",
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "1. 初始设置完成后，在同一项目中再创建一个 **OAuth 客户端 ID**。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "2. Select **iOS** as the **Application type** and set the **Bundle ID** to '**de.manhhao.hoshi**'." : {
      "comment" : "Context: Settings > Syncing. Surrounding UI explains Google Drive setup, then shows sync direction, auto-sync, Client ID, status, sign-out, and connect controls. Preserve product names and Markdown.",
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "2. 选择 **iOS** 作为 **应用类型**，并将 **Bundle ID** 设置为“**de.manhhao.hoshi**”。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "3. Paste the **Client ID** in the textbox below and press '**Connect Google Drive**'." : {
      "comment" : "Context: Settings > Syncing. Surrounding UI explains Google Drive setup, then shows sync direction, auto-sync, Client ID, status, sign-out, and connect controls. Preserve product names and Markdown.",
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "3. 将 **客户端 ID** 粘贴到下面的文本框中，然后点击“**连接 Google Drive**”。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "4. You can sync individual books by long-pressing and selecting '**Sync**'." : {
      "comment" : "Context: Settings > Syncing. Surrounding UI explains Google Drive setup, then shows sync direction, auto-sync, Client ID, status, sign-out, and connect controls. Preserve product names and Markdown.",
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "4. 你可以长按单本书并选择“**同步**”来同步。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "A **[Google Cloud project](https://github.com/ttu-ttu/ebook-reader?tab=readme-ov-file#storage-sources)** is necessary for syncing." : {
      "comment" : "Context: Settings > Syncing. Surrounding UI explains Google Drive setup, then shows sync direction, auto-sync, Client ID, status, sign-out, and connect controls. Preserve product names and Markdown.",
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "需要创建一个 **[Google Cloud 项目](https://github.com/ttu-ttu/ebook-reader?tab=readme-ov-file#storage-sources)** 进行同步。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
